keywords:
  - inverse problem
  - Tikhonov regularization
  - non-identifiability
  - transfer operator
  - Markov chain
  - multicluster system
  - least action
  - null-space projection
  - optimal transport
  - Sinkhorn
  - time-series forecasting
  - reproducibility
  - labour-market segmentation
  - radiation reaction
